      "functional_behavior": "Generate three independent single-ended PWM channels on TOM1 at 20 kHz, center-aligned, with duties initialized to U=25%, V=50%, W=75% and stepped by +10% every 500 ms with wrap from 100% to 0%, keeping active-high polarity and reusing TOM1 CH2/CH4/CH6 HS pins.",
